Thanks for using Faladdin! In this update, there are a few minor fixes and tweaks to fix stability and performance. Enjoy!

Here we come! The new Faladdin experience is ready for you!

From the beginning of our journey, our number one priority has always been to offer you an excellent fortune-telling experience. Bearing this in mind, we’ve been working hard for the last couple of months on the enhanced version of Faladdin. There are so many remarkable improvements, but the most significant one is our new design! It’s modern, it’s useful, and beyond dispute, it’s extremely entertaining!

We hope you will enjoy the new Faladdin as much as we enjoyed designing and developing it for you! Also, stay tuned for the next updates!

Be sure to try our newest content Biorhythm to find out the luck in romance, money, career, travel, and home life! Also, it is free of charge for a short period!
